data.description: Welcome to the epitome of luxury living in Middletown, NY, within the sought-after Maple Fields community. This meticulously designed 3-bed, 3-bath townhome offers a harmonious blend of elegance and functionality. Step into a spacious living area, seamlessly connected to a modern kitchen featuring sleek finishes and top-of-the-line appliances. The heart of this home, the kitchen, is perfect for culinary enthusiasts and casual meals. The three well-appointed bedrooms provide comfort and tranquility, and the unique Jack and Jill bathroom setup adds both convenience and a touch of sophistication. This thoughtful design ensures privacy while fostering a sense of unity among residents.  Location is paramount, and this townhome excels in proximity. Enjoy the convenience of nearby shopping, vibrant nightlife, and an array of restaurants catering to every taste. The renowned Galleria Mall is just a stone's throw away, offering premier shopping experiences and entertainment, Orange Counties primary hospital, Garnet Health Care is only minutes away. For those who value an active lifestyle, transportation hubs and gyms are easily accessible, ensuring you stay connected and fit. Commuting is a breeze with transportation close by, allowing you to make the most of your time at work and at play. In the heart of it all, this townhome invites you to experience the convenience and luxury of Community living. Don't miss the opportunity to call this place home schedule a viewing today and elevate your lifestyle in one of Middletown's most desirable communities!
